Author: fluentsyntax
Text: i used the word ‘therapy’ because i’m not in a position to see a professional about this bullshit right now. it’s too exhausting to search at the moment and i honestly don’t give a fuck about paying strangers to tell me what i already know. yes, i realize they can help me with proper methods and coping tools and what not, but i just... don’t care to talk to anyone currently. no energy.

Author: anonchicago7
Text: I'm just glad you feel you have a place to reach out.
